'''Raymond Jafelice''' is a writer, director, artist, and actor. He served as director and storyboard artist for many episodes of [[Ewoks (television series)|''Ewoks'']]. He is also known for his work in television shows such as ''Babar'', ''Little Bear'', ''Care Bears'', ''Strawberry Shortcake'', ''Redwall'', and more.

